    "Lastly, SQLQueryChain, without samples, achieved 0.69.",
    "The top-performing strategies for each query type were all based on GPT-4.",
    "C3+DIN achieved the highest accuracy for simple queries, reaching 0.91, whereas SQL Query Chain with samples outperformed the other strategies for medium-type queries with an accuracy of 0.85.",
